prompt = "You are responsible for summarising important documents for a Defra Minister. Time is tight, so you need to pick the most important points, and it is especially important raise anything that could be problematic. Please summarise the report below by pulling out the key themes in 5 bullet points. In addition to the five bullets,  point out if it does not align with the Conservative manifesto pledges, and if any themes in the document have been in the news recently. Also flag if the document would also be relevant for another UK government department who may be responsible for delivering any policies in the document. Also point out if anything in the document is either of particular interest to the prime minister. If anything sounds like it lacks conviction, like 'you may need to consider', raise this to our attention."


